premium/israels-ag-reprimanded-for-not-investigating-sale-of-pegasus-spyware-to-ghana/0000018c-fdff-d832-a59d-fdff63900000</guid></item><item><title>“严重扭曲”：以色列在世界法院听证会上拒绝加沙种族灭绝指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</link><description>以色列呼吁国际法院以毫无根据为由驳回该案，并驳回南非关于停止以色列国防军在加沙行动的请愿。以色列代表：整个案件“取决于对现实的故意策划、脱节和操纵性描述”</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院听证会上，以色列尽管政客愚笨，但仍提出强有力的辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</link><description>海牙的种族灭绝事件并不是由不成比例的军事反应或大量巴勒斯坦人伤亡引发的。这是以色列政治特征的直接结果：鲁莽和煽动性的冗长，而以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对此予以纵容。他甚至添加了一些自己的宝石</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的“战线统一”也增强了伊朗国内代理人的地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</link><description>真主党、也门胡塞武装和伊拉克什叶派民兵组织已经在国内的战斗中取得了成果，而且他们并不打算在加沙战争结束后停止。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</guid></item><item><title>一系列失败证明以色列安全理念已经过时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</link><description>情报一次又一次失败，现在两线作战，平民后方遭受前所未有的攻势。以色列国防军的威慑力曾有效应对 20 世纪 60 年代的威胁，但如今需要不同的解决方案。旧制度已经破产</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 13:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</guid></item><item><title>五十万加沙人正在遭受严重饥饿。让其沉入其中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</link><description>加沙危机的范围变得越来越清晰；据联合国称，以色列正在创造条件，使加沙的生活变得不可能；但以色列领导人却毫不在意</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</guid></item><item><title>3亿年前早期爬行动物的皮肤化石展示了从海洋到陆地的转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-12/ty-article/earliest-skin-fossil-showcases-transition-from-sea-to-land/0000018c-fd0d-d2fd-a3ae-fd0f8bcc0000</link><description>爬行动物祖先的指甲大小的皮肤是迄今为止在陆地动物身上发现的最早的皮肤化石，可能展示了原始状态</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 10:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-12/ty-article/earliest-skin-fossil-showcases-transition-from-sea-to-land/0000018c-fd0d-d2fd-a3ae-fd0f8bcc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡永无休止的任期是以色列的毒瘤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</link><description>随着以色列与哈马斯的战争即将进入第 100 天，政府必须将遣返人质作为首要任务 - 即使以停火为代价。 ■ 哈马斯通过其外交/法律手段将以色列拖到国际法院开普敦代理——突显内塔尼亚胡政府在各方面的失败程度</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-never-ending-tenure-is-israels-malignant-disease/0000018c-fa20-d517-af9d-fe3e08560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争已接近100天。未来还有很多天的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</link><description>哈马斯正在顽强抵抗，而以色列国防军远未实现其目标 ■ 以色列对新人质协议说“不”可能会导致他们的灭亡 ■ 美国国务卿为第二天制定了自己的计划 - 但有一个小问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/digging-in-hamas-isnt-giving-up-idf-far-from-achieving-its-goals/0000018c-f9d3-dd94-a9cc-fbff27910000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹袭击以色列南部；以色列国防军在约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，击毙 3 名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</link><description>以色列国防军称，约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，三名恐怖分子被打死。 ■ 火箭警报在阿什杜德、加沙边境附近以及黎巴嫩边境沿线响起。 ■ 以色列国防军表示，将启动军事机制，调查加沙涉嫌违反国际法的行为。 ■ 在对红海航运进行数月袭击后，美国和英国在也门打击了伊朗支持的胡塞武装；胡塞武装发誓这次袭击不会逍遥法外 ■ 黎巴嫩总理表示，不包括加沙停火的协议毫无意义；从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射的反坦克导弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-live/israel-to-counter-south-african-genocide-accusations-at-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-fbaa-dd94-a9cc-fbeeb7c10000</guid></item><item><title>“在我按照与生俱来的权利去以色列旅行之前，我并不关心自己是不是犹太人。然后我的整个世界都变了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名美国人在遇到一系列先知后决定成为一名拉比，而一个以色列家庭在父亲完成加沙几个月的预备役后正在休息</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-12/ty-article/.highlight/i-didnt-care-about-being-jewish-until-i-went-on-birthright-my-whole-world-changed/0000018c-fb82-dd94-a9cc-fbee842a0000</guid></item><item><title>台上台下，奥哈德·纳哈林在加沙战争中传达了强有力的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</link><description>“人们称我为以色列的诽谤者，但诽谤以色列这个定居者救世主右翼的是我们的政府。他们认为以色列国防军的行动应该继续下去，士兵和人质的死亡是可以理解的代价。巴特谢瓦舞蹈团编舞家奥哈德·纳哈林拒绝闭嘴跳舞</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/on-stage-and-off-ohad-naharin-conveys-a-powerful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：伊朗是胡塞武装和其他组织袭击以色列的主要推动者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</link><description>在此之前，美国领导的联军袭击也门胡塞武装目标，以回应数月来对红海海上交通的袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列人回忆起他们在哈马斯被囚禁期间的磨难：“每天都有人在身体和灵魂上杀死一些东西”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</link><description>战争已经过去近 100 天了，而且还被关押在加沙地带。七名人质返回，但将父母、孩子、兄弟姐妹和朋友留在加沙，描述了他们所经历的一切，并敦促采取一切措施立即将剩余的俘虏带回家</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 00:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/seven-israelis-recall-their-ordeal-in-hamas-captivity-every-day-kills-something-inside/0000018c-f9d9-dd94-a9cc-fbfd31340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方禁止针对加沙战争的抗议活动，理由是无法保护公众、防止暴力，</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</link><description>人权组织猛烈抨击阻止犹太和阿拉伯团体在海法示威的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 22:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-bars-protests-against-gaza-war-says-police-cant-protect-public-prevent-violence/0000018c-fa19-d1b3-a79e-fedbd1e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长可能无法避免对内塔尼亚胡是否适合任职的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</link><description>几个月后，如果内塔尼亚胡政府仍然完好无损，总理将不得不每天花几个小时在审判中作证，同时还要管理国家 ■ 最高法院可能已经停止了司法改革，但对裁决的仔细审查也令人担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 21:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-may-not-be-able-to-avoid-ruling-on-netanyahus-fitness-for-office/0000018c-fa0a-dd94-a9cc-faee69fb0000</guid></item><item><title>南非是否已经破坏了以色列对国际法院种族灭绝指控的辩护？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-11/ty-article/.highlight/has-south-africa-already-wrecked-israels-defense-against-icj-charges-of-genocide/0000018c-f9cc-d1b3-a79e-ffded2f10000</link><description>以色列的自卫并未受到审判，也不能成为违反《种族灭绝公约》任何部分的理由。简而言之，以色列的国防几乎没有提供任何防御</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 20:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-11/ty-article/.highlight/has-south-africa-already-wrecked-israels-defense-against-icj-charges-of-genocide/0000018c-f9cc-d1b3-a79e-ffded2f10000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔即将与哈马斯敲定协议，向加沙的以色列人质运送药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/qatar-close-to-finalizing-deal-with-hamas-to-transfer-medicine-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018c-f9e9-dd94-a9cc-fbed7be90000</link><description>据报道，该协议包括以色列允许更多药品进入加沙，以换取向以色列人质提供处方药</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 19:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/qatar-close-to-finalizing-deal-with-hamas-to-transfer-medicine-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018c-f9e9-dd94-a9cc-fbed7be90000</guid></item></channel></rss>